/11]]<br/>\n{{legend|lime|Win}}\n{{legend|yellow|Top 10}}\n{{legend|#eeeeee|Did not play}}\nQF, R16, R32, R64 = Round in which player lost in match play<br/>\n\"T\" = tied<br/>\nNT = No Tournament<br/>\nThe HSBC Champions did not become a WGC event until 2009.\n\n==PGA Tour career summary==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n!Season!!Wins (Majors)!!Earnings ($)!!Rank\n|-\n|[[1991 PGA Tour|1991]] || 1 || 0<sup>\u2020</sup> || {{n/a}}\n|-\n|[[1992 PGA Tour|1992]] || 0 || 171,714 || 90\n|-\n|[[1993 PGA Tour|1993]] || 2 || 628,735 || 22\n|-\n|[[1994 PGA Tour|1994]] || 1 || 748,316 || 15\n|-\n|[[1995 PGA Tour|1995]] || 1 || 655,777 || 28\n|-\n|[[1996 PGA Tour|1996]] || 4 || 1,697,799 || style=\"background:yellow;\"|2\n|-\n|[[1997 PGA Tour|1997]] || 2 || 1,225,390 || 11\n|-\n|[[1998 PGA Tour|1998]] || 2 || 1,837,246 || style=\"background:yellow;\"|6\n|-\n|[[1999 PGA Tour|1999]] || 0 || 1,722,681 || 14\n|-\n|[[2000 PGA Tour|2000]] || 4 || 4,746,457 || style=\"background:yellow;\"|2\n|-\n|[[2001 PGA Tour|2001]] || 2 || 4,403,833 || style=\"background:yellow;\"|2\n|-\n|[[2002 PGA Tour|2002]] || 2 || 4,311,971 || style=\"background:yellow;\"|2\n|-\n|[[2003 PGA Tour|2003]] || 0 || 1,623,137 || 38\n|-\n|[[2004 PGA Tour|2004]] || 2 (1) || 5,784,823 || style=\"background:yellow;\"|3\n|-\n|[[2005 PGA Tour|2005]] || 4 (1) || 5,699,605 || style=\"background:yellow;\"|3\n|-\n|[[2006 PGA Tour|2006]] || 2 (1) || 4,256,505 || style=\"background:yellow;\"|6\n|-\n|[[2007 PGA Tour|2007]] || 3 || 5,819,988 || style=\"background:yellow;\"|2\n|-\n|[[2008 PGA Tour|2008]] || 2 || 5,118,875 || style=\"background:yellow;\"|3\n|-\n|[[2009 PGA Tour|2009]] || 3 || 5,332,755 || style=\"background:yellow;\"|3\n|-\n|[[2010 PGA Tour|2010]] || 1 (1) || 3,821,733 || style=\"background:yellow;\"|6\n|-\n|[[2011 PGA Tour|2011]] || 1 || 3,763,488 || 12\n|-\n|[[2012 PGA Tour|2012]] || 1 || 4,203,821 || style=\"background:yellow;\"|8\n|-\n|[[2013 PGA Tour|2013]] || 2 (1) || 5,495,793 || style=